flowchart TD
    AD1[Load pending POI queue] --> AD2[Inspect POI + audio]
    AD2 --> AD3{Decision}
    AD3 -- Approve --> AD4[Set Approved]
    AD3 -- Reject --> AD5[Set Rejected + reason]
    AD3 -- Lock --> AD6[Set Locked + reason]
    AD3 -- Unlock --> AD7[Set Approved]
    AD4 --> AD8[Notify saler]
    AD5 --> AD8
    AD6 --> AD8
    AD7 --> AD8
    AD8 --> AD9[Refresh counters and lists]
